# Large trained checkpoints kept locally but not pushed (multi-GB; regenerable
# from the training scripts). Tournament result JSONs + sweep tables stay tracked.
# Exception: keep the FINAL model of each run tracked (~27M/23M) so smoke tests
# can load+run a real checkpoint on other devices. (! negation un-ignores them;
# the dir line must NOT have a trailing slash for the negation to apply.)
models/checkpoints/ppo_512x512x256_50m/*
!models/checkpoints/ppo_512x512x256_50m/ppo_final.zip
models/checkpoints/sp_league_200m_512/*
!models/checkpoints/sp_league_200m_512/selfplay_final.zip
